{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/writing/how-to-be-empty/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Chandler Moisen","author":"Chandler Moisen"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6d485d28-ca4a-5e2f-9d9e-4604d45bef7b","excerpt":"In an effort to bring order to the chaos that is transferring medical records between doctors, I recently signed up for Galileo Health.  Purporting to simplify…","html":"<p>In an effort to bring order to the chaos that is transferring medical records between doctors, I recently signed up for <a href=\"https://galileohealth.com/\">Galileo Health</a>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ce750a31540a6ea4a78c5d2cf7d43646/0c307/galileo_health_landing.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.78378378378378%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"galileo health landing\"\n        title=\"galileo health landing\"\n        src=\"/static/ce750a31540a6ea4a78c5d2cf7d43646/fcda8/galileo_health_landing.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ce750a31540a6ea4a78c5d2cf7d43646/12f09/galileo_health_landing.png 148w,\n/static/ce750a31540a6ea4a78c5d2cf7d43646/e4a3f/galileo_health_landing.png 295w,\n/static/ce750a31540a6ea4a78c5d2cf7d43646/fcda8/galileo_health_landing.png 590w,\n/static/ce750a31540a6ea4a78c5d2cf7d43646/efc66/galileo_health_landing.png 885w,\n/static/ce750a31540a6ea4a78c5d2cf7d43646/c83ae/galileo_health_landing.png 1180w,\n/static/ce750a31540a6ea4a78c5d2cf7d43646/0c307/galileo_health_landing.png 2526w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Purporting to simplify management of personal electronic health records, Galileo also helps users schedule simple check-ups, renew prescriptions (that are not controlled substances), request lab work, and other tedious personal health tasks.</p>\n<h2>Overlooking Emptiness</h2>\n<p>While the Galileo application has a nice user experience overall, the search functionality leaves a bit to be desired.</p>\n<p>This is the result of searching for the NYU Langone hospital system:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 211px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1161ad33a0fa94a9e299269242931cf4/4050c/galileo_empty_results.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 177.7027027027027%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"galileo empty results\"\n        title=\"galileo empty results\"\n        src=\"/static/1161ad33a0fa94a9e299269242931cf4/4050c/galileo_empty_results.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1161ad33a0fa94a9e299269242931cf4/12f09/galileo_empty_results.png 148w,\n/static/1161ad33a0fa94a9e299269242931cf4/4050c/galileo_empty_results.png 211w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 211px) 100vw, 211px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Just a nebulous empty-state containing the text: <em>Search for “NYU Langone”</em> - an action which I believed had just occurred.</p>\n<p>Galileo can be forgiven for not having every single doctor and hospital available on their platform, but they should be taking advantage of this empty-state to give the user better feedback.</p>\n<p>This got me curious to how other products display empty search results.</p>\n<h2>The Art of Being Empty</h2>\n<h3>Clear Copy</h3>\n<p>At the very least, users need an unequivocal response that their search has not returned any results.</p>\n<p>The developer-focused blogging platform <a href=\"https://dev.to\">dev.to</a> does this well:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/44e389718108289b540c1d92810635d9/5ab15/dev_to_empty_results.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.324324324324326%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"dev to empty results\"\n        title=\"dev to empty results\"\n        src=\"/static/44e389718108289b540c1d92810635d9/fcda8/dev_to_empty_results.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/44e389718108289b540c1d92810635d9/12f09/dev_to_empty_results.png 148w,\n/static/44e389718108289b540c1d92810635d9/e4a3f/dev_to_empty_results.png 295w,\n/static/44e389718108289b540c1d92810635d9/fcda8/dev_to_empty_results.png 590w,\n/static/44e389718108289b540c1d92810635d9/efc66/dev_to_empty_results.png 885w,\n/static/44e389718108289b540c1d92810635d9/c83ae/dev_to_empty_results.png 1180w,\n/static/44e389718108289b540c1d92810635d9/5ab15/dev_to_empty_results.png 2446w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Simple Suggestions</h3>\n<p>Even better, add some light copy to encourage the user to try different approaches to their search as we see with <a href=\"https://spotify.com\">Spotify</a>:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e5a511adde3b60459d1dc5d97c897c67/cd536/spotify_empty_results.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.4054054054054%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"spotify empty results\"\n        title=\"spotify empty results\"\n        src=\"/static/e5a511adde3b60459d1dc5d97c897c67/fcda8/spotify_empty_results.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e5a511adde3b60459d1dc5d97c897c67/12f09/spotify_empty_results.png 148w,\n/static/e5a511adde3b60459d1dc5d97c897c67/e4a3f/spotify_empty_results.png 295w,\n/static/e5a511adde3b60459d1dc5d97c897c67/fcda8/spotify_empty_results.png 590w,\n/static/e5a511adde3b60459d1dc5d97c897c67/efc66/spotify_empty_results.png 885w,\n/static/e5a511adde3b60459d1dc5d97c897c67/cd536/spotify_empty_results.png 1114w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://google.com\">Google’s search</a> renders a similar empty-state:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2be39129042833b218383aefbac393d2/7a18f/google_empty_results.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"google empty results\"\n        title=\"google empty results\"\n        src=\"/static/2be39129042833b218383aefbac393d2/fcda8/google_empty_results.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2be39129042833b218383aefbac393d2/12f09/google_empty_results.png 148w,\n/static/2be39129042833b218383aefbac393d2/e4a3f/google_empty_results.png 295w,\n/static/2be39129042833b218383aefbac393d2/fcda8/google_empty_results.png 590w,\n/static/2be39129042833b218383aefbac393d2/efc66/google_empty_results.png 885w,\n/static/2be39129042833b218383aefbac393d2/c83ae/google_empty_results.png 1180w,\n/static/2be39129042833b218383aefbac393d2/7a18f/google_empty_results.png 1284w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Actionable</h3>\n<p>My favorite empty-state is <a href=\"https://amazon.com\">Amazon’s e-commerce search results</a>.</p>\n<p>Not only is the user provided with clear copy and simple suggestions on how to alter their search, but Amazon also affords the user the opportunity to provide valuable feedback:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1d4102e6daf9b0c7ff9df7e63a78f62b/9239a/amazon_empty_results.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.972972972972975%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"amazon empty results\"\n        title=\"amazon empty results\"\n        src=\"/static/1d4102e6daf9b0c7ff9df7e63a78f62b/fcda8/amazon_empty_results.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d4102e6daf9b0c7ff9df7e63a78f62b/12f09/amazon_empty_results.png 148w,\n/static/1d4102e6daf9b0c7ff9df7e63a78f62b/e4a3f/amazon_empty_results.png 295w,\n/static/1d4102e6daf9b0c7ff9df7e63a78f62b/fcda8/amazon_empty_results.png 590w,\n/static/1d4102e6daf9b0c7ff9df7e63a78f62b/efc66/amazon_empty_results.png 885w,\n/static/1d4102e6daf9b0c7ff9df7e63a78f62b/c83ae/amazon_empty_results.png 1180w,\n/static/1d4102e6daf9b0c7ff9df7e63a78f62b/9239a/amazon_empty_results.png 1246w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Whether users are actually using this feature is another question…</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How To Be Empty","date":"May 29, 2019","isTIL":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/how-to-be-empty/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/curiosity-and-why-react-needs-to-be-in-scope/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Curiosity and Why JSX Requires React in Scope","redirects":["/curiosity-and-why-react-needs-to-be-in-scope"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/customer-problems-vs-business-problems/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Customer Problems vs. Business Problems","redirects":["/customer-problems-vs-business-problems"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["4173562750","63159454"]}